```plantuml
@startuml jinnerbichler_flash-home
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "Home Assistant" as HA {
}

rectangle "Coffee Machine Client" as CoffeeClient #lightyellow

rectangle "Flash Server" as FlashServer #lightsteelblue {
  rectangle "Coffee Machine Flash Server" as CMFlashServer #aliceblue
  rectangle "Provider Flash Server" as ProviderFlashServer #aliceblue
}

rectangle "IOTA Testnet" as IOTANetwork #mistyrose

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> HA : trigger actions (make coffee,\ninitialize/fund/close channel)

' Home Assistant interactions
HA <--> CoffeeClient : MQTT communication\n(trigger coffee actions, receive status)

' Coffee Machine Client interactions
CoffeeClient --> CMFlashServer : initiate payment\nsign transactions
CMFlashServer --> ProviderFlashServer : sign transactions\nsettle payments

' Flash Server interactions
CMFlashServer <--> IOTANetwork : interact with Tangle\n(create/close channels)
ProviderFlashServer <--> IOTANetwork : interact with Tangle\n(process transactions)

@enduml
```